                <div class="catalog-panel catalog-panel--about">
                    <blockquote class="catalog-quote"><strong>By Alisa Khru</strong> is a contemporary gallery demo: esoteric surfaces, archival grain, and one electric accent on monochrome matter — a browser-native nod to exhibition design.</blockquote>
